    <section id="tei_odd_dragdrop_actions">
      <title>TEI ODD Drag/Drop Actions</title>
      <p id="p_gkk_cgk_54b">Dragging a file from the <xref href="using-the-project-view.dita#using-the-project-view"
          format="dita"><uicontrol product="author editor">Project</uicontrol><uicontrol
            product="authorEclipse editorEclipse">Project Explorer</uicontrol> view</xref> and dropping it
        into a TEI ODD document that is edited in <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode, creates a link
        to the dragged file (the <xmlelement>ptr</xmlelement> element with the
          <xmlatt>target</xmlatt> attribute) at the drop location.</p>
    </section>
